Effective Date: January 3, 2025
1. Introduction
[Kingset Game] ("we," "us," or "our") values your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and share your information when you use our gaming application ("Services"). By using our Services, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
2. Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information to provide and improve our Services:
1) Personal Information
- Name, username, email address, phone number, and unique user identifiers.
2) Device Information
- Details about your device, such as model, operating system, language, and unique device ID.
3) Usage Information
- Details of how you interact with our Services, including gameplay data, app settings, and error logs.
4) Location Information
- Geographical data (collected only with your explicit consent).
5) Payment Information
- Billing details (e.g., card numbers, transaction history) when you make in-app purchases.
3. How We Use Your Information
Your information is used for purposes such as:
1）Providing Services: Ensuring the functionality and reliability of the application.
2）Personalization: Tailoring content, gameplay suggestions, and ads to your preferences.
3）Customer Support: Responding to inquiries and resolving issues.
4）Analytics and Improvements: Monitoring performance and user trends to enhance services.
5）Compliance: Meeting legal and regulatory requirements.
4. Information Sharing and Disclosure
We may share your data only in the following circumstances:
1）With Service Providers: Trusted partners assisting in app functionality, such as cloud hosting or analytics.
2）For Legal Obligations: When required to comply with legal obligations or court orders.
3）In Business Transfers: As part of a merger, acquisition, or sale of company assets.
4）With Your Consent: If you explicitly authorize data sharing.
5. Information Retention and Deletion
1）Retention Period:
- Your information is retained as long as necessary to provide our Services or as required by law.
2）Deletion:
- You may request deletion of your account and personal data by contacting us at
creatadev07@outlook.com
.
6. Data Security
We employ advanced security measures such as encryption and access restrictions to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or misuse. However, no method is completely secure, and we encourage users to take precautions.
7. Children's Privacy
Our Services are not directed at children under 13. If we discover we have collected data from a child under 13 without parental consent, we will promptly delete such data.
8. Your Rights and Choices
Depending on your region, you may have the right to:
1）Access your personal information.
2）Correct inaccuracies in your data.
3）Request deletion of your data.
4）Opt-out of personalized advertisements.
5）Withdraw consent for data collection at any time.
To exercise these rights, contact us via
creatadev07@outlook.com
.
9. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any significant changes will be communicated through in-app notifications or email. Please review this policy regularly.
10. Contact Us
